{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840795420,"sessionID":"ses_287a46799ffe0U0W2ZegN3Kyn3","part":{"id":"prt_d785c1adf001mjwBiB9UJTQvpd","messageID":"msg_d785c0a96001y8OOjuQccxJ2x2","sessionID":"ses_287a46799ffe0U0W2ZegN3Kyn3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8d4d21e25ff24d44b3bfdf64dac598d2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","limit":50,"offset":30},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n30: - **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n31: \n32: ### CodeInterpreter\n33: \n34: `CodeInterpreter` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a code execution environment for managing interpreter sandboxes.\n35: \n36: #### Spec\n37: \n38: The `CodeInterpreterSpec` defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter:\n39: \n40: - **Image** (string, required): Container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\")\n41: - **Runtime** (string, optional): Execution environment type (default: \"python\")\n42:   - Allowed values: `python`, `javascript`, `typescript`, `go`\n43: - **Timeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum execution time for code snippets (default: 5m)\n44: - **Resources** (*SandboxContainerResources, optional): Compute resource requirements\n45: - **Env** ([]SandboxEnvVar, optional): Environment variables to inject\n46: - **EnabledPackages** ([]string, optional): Allowed packages for the interpreter\n47: \n48: #### Status\n49: \n50: The `CodeInterpreterStatus` defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter:\n51: \n52: - **Ready** (bool, optional): Whether the interpreter is ready to execute code\n53: - **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the interpreter state\n54: - **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n55: \n56: ### SandboxTemplate\n57: \n58: Defines the template for creating sandbox pods:\n59: \n60: - **Metadata** (*SandboxMetadata, optional): Labels and annotations for the pod\n61: - **Spec** (SandboxPodSpec, required): Pod specification\n62: \n63: ### SandboxPodSpec\n64: \n65: Defines the pod specification for sandbox pods:\n66: \n67: - **Containers** ([]SandboxContainer, required): List of containers in the pod\n68: - **NodeSelector** (map[string]string, optional): Node selection constraints\n69: - **Affinity** (*SandboxAffinity, optional): Pod scheduling constraints\n70: - **Tolerations** ([]SandboxToleration, optional): Pod tolerations\n71: - **ResourceRequirements** (*SandboxResources, optional): Resource requirements for the pod\n72: - **Volumes** ([]SandboxVolume, optional): Pod volumes\n73: \n74: ## Usage\n75: \n76: ### Creating an AgentRuntime\n77: \n78: ```yaml\n79: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n\n(Showing lines 30-79 of 260. Use offset=80 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n`CodeInterpreter` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a code execution environment for managing interpreter sandboxes.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterSpec` defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter:\n\n- **Image** (string, required): Container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\")\n- **Runtime** (string, optional): Execution environment type (default: \"python\")\n  - Allowed values: `python`, `javascript`, `typescript`, `go`\n- **Timeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum execution time for code snippets (default: 5m)\n- **Resources** (*SandboxContainerResources, optional): Compute resource requirements\n- **Env** ([]SandboxEnvVar, optional): Environment variables to inject\n- **EnabledPackages** ([]string, optional): Allowed packages for the interpreter\n\n#### Status\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","time":{"start":1775840795395,"end":1775840795418}}}}
